&gt;&gt; ...partner community to
deliver for our warfighters and

01:28:25.860 --> 01:28:29.260
defense leaders for when it
matters most.

01:28:29.260 --> 01:28:31.590
&gt;&gt; NARRATOR: Bezos himself has
made it clear that he sees

